    <item>
      <title>莫迪在没有证据的情况下指控阿达尼、安巴尼提供非法现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/modi-alleges-ambani-adani-giving-opposition-party-illegal-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理纳伦德拉·莫迪未经证实地指控印度主要反对党从亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼和高塔姆·阿达尼那里收受非法现金，在激烈的选举斗争中升级了他的言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/modi-alleges-ambani-adani-giving-opposition-party-illegal-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 08:16:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国在最新一次针对政客的袭击后处于高度戒备状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/german-authorities-on-alert-after-latest-attack-on-politician</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国当局拘留了一名涉嫌周二袭击柏林国务部长和前市长的 74 岁男子，这是下个月欧洲议会选举前政治暴力激增的最新证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/german-authorities-on-alert-after-latest-attack-on-politician</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 05:22:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国将在政策大转变中再次将大麻定为非法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/new-thai-health-minister-signals-rethink-of-cannabis-decriminalization-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛 (Srettha Thavisin) 下令彻底改变该国具有里程碑意义的大麻政策，称该植物应很快再次被归类为麻醉品，其用途仅限于医疗和健康目的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/new-thai-health-minister-signals-rethink-of-cannabis-decriminalization-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:06:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克正在与欧洲极右翼接触，但选民不太确定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/musk-is-engaging-with-europe-s-far-right-but-voters-aren-t-so-sure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲极右翼政党备受关注，包括与埃隆·马斯克在社交媒体上的互动。但推动他们成为国际关注焦点的争议也给民意调查带来了代价，因为他们在六月的欧洲选举中难以保持势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/musk-is-engaging-with-europe-s-far-right-but-voters-aren-t-so-sure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯恢复对乌克兰电网的“大规模”攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ukraine-s-kyiv-lviv-under-attack-after-more-than-1-month-pause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯在暂停两周后恢复对乌克兰电力生产和配电网络的攻击，目标是全国各地的设施，包括首都和西部靠近波兰边境的利沃夫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ukraine-s-kyiv-lviv-under-attack-after-more-than-1-month-pause</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 03:57:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
